OL,3,CFujitsu staff 'dragged over coals' if
OL,4,Cthey admitted issues with Horizon
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV News, a
OL,8,FFujitsu whistleblower revealed how
OL,9,Fstaff dreaded taking calls on
OL,10,FWednesdays - the day post offices were
OL,11,Frequired to balance their accounts. UK
OL,12,FEditor Paul Brand reports
OL,14,FA former employee at a Fujitsu call
OL,15,Fcentre who dealt with queries from sub-
OL,16,Fpostmasters about the Horizon system
OL,17,Ftold ITV News that staff would have
OL,18,Fbeen "dragged over the coals" if they
OL,19,Fadmitted the software had problems.
