OL,7,FNate Orrow worked at Fujitsu's
OL,8,FStevenage call centre for two years,
OL,9,Fbetween 2010 and 2012.
OL,11,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV News, he
OL,12,Fsaid that when sub-postmasters were
OL,13,Frequired to balance their accounts,
OL,14,Fthe call centre would be "back to back
OL,15,Ffor hours" with queries.
OL,17,F"There was no respite from the
OL,18,Fqueueing calls", he said.
OL,20,F"The bulk of it was account
OL,21,Fdiscrepancies," Mr Orrow added.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/10
