OL,7,F"More often than not it was a mystery.
OL,8,FThe most you could do was try to
OL,9,Fempathise with them, comfort them and
OL,10,Fsay you'd escalate it up.
OL,12,F"It was difficult talking to people,
OL,13,Fsome of the people were pretty
OL,14,Fdesperate."
OL,16,F'We hated supporting it, it was a bad
OL,17,Fpiece of software. If anyone did say
OL,18,Fanything and their call was listened
OL,19,Fto they would be dragged over the
OL,20,Fcoals'
