OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FMr Orrow said call centre staff
OL,8,Fregularly discussed the fact that
OL,9,FHorizon "was obviously a dreadful
OL,10,Fpiece of software" - though they
OL,11,Fweren't certain of its specific faults.
OL,13,F"We were under no illusion that the
OL,14,Fsystem wasn't good. We hated
OL,15,Fsupporting it. It was a bad piece of
OL,16,Fsoftware", he said.
OL,18,FBut Mr Orrow alleged that staff would
OL,19,Fbe punished for letting on to sub-
OL,20,Fpostmasters that there were problems
OL,21,Fwith the system.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/10
