OL,7,F"If anybody ever made any kind of
OL,8,Fsuggestion that that was the case
OL,9,Fthey'd be dragged over the coals if
OL,10,Fthe call was listened to or a
OL,11,Fsupervisor overheard them."
OL,13,FMr Orrow is the first Horizon call
OL,14,Fhandler to be interviewed by the media
OL,15,Fsince the recent
OL,17,F"Naturally you feel a little bit of
OL,18,Fsecond-hand guilt, because maybe I
OL,19,Fcould have done something different",
OL,20,Fhe told us.
