OL,7,F"Hindsight is great, but I have no
OL,8,Fdoubts looking back at it now that it
OL,9,Fwas obviously a dreadful piece of
OL,10,Fsoftware that was causing these
OL,11,Fproblems."
OL,13,F"I genuinely wish I hadn't worked
OL,14,Fthere. I wish I'd been put on a
OL,15,Fdifferent account at the very least."
