OL,7,F'Everyone was crying out for help.
OL,8,FThey made us look like idiots': Former
OL,9,Fsub-postmaster Harjinder Butoy told
OL,10,FITV News UK Editor Paul Brand after
OL,11,Fthe Post Office accused him of
OL,12,Fstealing #200,000 and being sentenced
OL,13,Fto three years in prison
OL,15,FFormer sub-postmaster Harjinder Butoy
OL,16,Fwas one of those who said he
OL,17,Frepeatedly called the Horizon helpdesk.
OL,19,FEventually, the Post Office accused
OL,20,Fhim of stealing #200,000 and he was
OL,21,Fsentenced to three years in prison.
