OL,7,FReacting to Mr Orrow's interview, he
OL,8,Fexpressed anger at Fujitsu and Post
OL,9,FOffice management.
OL,11,FMr Butoy said: "It is absolutely
OL,12,Fwrong, this is absolutely shocking.
OL,13,FPeople said we never asked for help,
OL,14,Feveryone was crying out for help from
OL,15,Fthe help desk.
OL,17,F"Maybe they (Fujitsu) knew it. They
OL,18,Fhave made us look like thick idiots."
