OL,7,FIn response to the latest claims, a
OL,8,FFujitsu spokesperson told ITV News:
OL,9,F"The Fujitsu Group regards this matter
OL,10,Fwith the utmost seriousness and offers
OL,11,Fits deepest apologies to the sub-
OL,12,Fpostmasters and their families.
OL,14,F"The UK statutory public Inquiry, to
OL,15,Fwhich our UK subsidiary is providing
OL,16,Ffull cooperation, is examining complex
OL,17,Fevents that have unfolded over many
OL,18,Fyears, and we remain steadfast in our
OL,19,Fcommitment to this cooperation.
